  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy, safety and tolerability of AEB071 in the treatment of
      active, moderate to severe ulcerative colitis in patients who have failed conventional
      therapy using mesalamine or steroids
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
